data.description: Stunning 3 bedroom 2 1/2 bath home located in the beautiful gated community of “The Peninsula” in Gulf Shores, Alabama! The property sits on a large lot at the end of a cul-de-sac and borders 179’ of wooded area giving you lots of privacy and beautiful golf course views! The Peninsula also offers a 27 hole golf course on over 800 acres of the most amazing nature preserved areas in town. As you enter the home the high living room ceilings and all the welcoming openness of the home will take your breath away. Not to mention all the views and lighting the numerous windows has to offer! The updated kitchen brings elegance with the see-thru glass cabinet doors and the smooth flow of the colors on your granite countertops!  The large living room brings back the classic and luxurious vibes with the granite surrounded gas fire place and a first class built in entertainment center including a wet bar and a wine rack which all reflects on the pristine wooden floors of this cozy family gathering space. A new roof recently installed in 2019 and a new HVAC compressor in 2022 this amazing property has so much to offer! Seller also has an assumable loan with interest of 5.625% if applicable to Buyer!  Call today and schedule a showing!
